                  </span></div><br><div class="comment">
                  <span class="c00">&gt;I don&#x27;t think of a reading TODO as &quot;food&quot; such that you should eat the old food before the new food. (The old food will expire so it makes sense to consume that first.)<p>Based on this explanation, maybe you should. News and information often decrease in usefulness and relevance the longer you wait to digest it.<span>
